# GitHub Backend Assignment

A backend service built with **Node.js**, **Express**, and **TypeScript** following the **Repository Pattern**.  
This app integrates with the GitHub API and provides APIs for saving users, finding friends (mutual followers), searching, updating, deleting, and sorting user data.  

---

## 🚀 Features
- Save GitHub user details to database (avoid duplicate API calls)  
- Find mutual followers (friends)  
- Search users by username, location, etc.  
- Soft delete user records  
- Update user profile fields (bio, blog, location, etc.)  
- List users sorted by followers, repos, etc.  
- Input validation & error handling  
- Repository-based architecture  
- Unit & Integration tests with Jest  

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- **Node.js** + **Express**  
- **TypeScript**  
- **TypeORM / SQLite** (or your chosen DB)  
- **Axios** (for GitHub API calls)  
- **Jest** + **Supertest** (testing)  

